external_knowledge:
- 'Troublemakers' refers to players who have received at least one yellow card (yellow_cards > 0); 
- 'Scoring potential per match' refers to expected goals per 90 minutes (xG_per90); 
- 'Scoring expectations' refers to total expected goals (expected_goals); 
- 'Influence on the game' refers to the overall influence score of the player (influence); 
- 'Distances they've covered' refers to the total distance run by the player in kilometers (distance_run); 
- 'Ranked by their scoring prowess' refers to ordering the results by expected goals per 90 minutes in descending order (ORDER BY xG_per90 DESC).

sql:
SELECT injury_type, recovery_time 
FROM injury_reports 
WHERE injury_severity = 'minor' AND recovery_time = 7;

SELECT MAX(expected_goals) 
FROM advanced_stats 
WHERE player_id = 1;
